-----
Usage
-----

Add script to a HTML document that contains slides using the following format:

  <section typeof="http://purl.org/ontology/bibo/Slide">
    Slide content here
    <details>
      Slide notes here
    </details>
  </section>

For image slides use:

  <section typeof="http://purl.org/ontology/bibo/Slide">
    <img class="fill" src="filename">
    <details>
      Slide notes here
    </details>
  </section>



Based on DZ Slides - http://paulrouget.com/dzslides/